# Insulin Lispro Biosimilar

## Overview

Rapid-acting insulin biosimilar equivalent to Humalog with faster onset of prandial glucose control.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Lispro Biosimilar |

## Mechanism of Action

Proline-B28 to lysine-B28 substitution prevents dimerization enabling rapid absorption; biosimilar development ensures identical amino acid sequence and pharmacokinetics.

